JSON -> XML:

- value as an actual XML prop name (FIXED: Changed to @value)
i.e.
{
    "Test": {
        "attribute": "a1",
        "value": "a2",
        "@value": "v" 
    }
} 
<Test attribute="a1" value="a2">
    v
</Test>

- value type check? int, str, bool, array, null
i.e.
{
    "Test": null
}

- attribute-value pair is not of type str, int, bool, null
i.e.
{
    "attribute": {}
}